<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab>Als wir ew nehst <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> der ladung wegen, als Hans
                                <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> auf die lantschrann gen
                                <expan>Hirsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, wie uns Hans
                                <expan>Newstet<ex>er</ex></expan> und Hans Steczman,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, als die <add>vormals</add>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> darumb bey ew gewesen sind, wol gesagt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir ew
                            <expan>dary<ex>n</ex>ne</expan> gar gelimppflich <app>
<note place="interlinear">a</note>
</app> etc. <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kunden</expan>. <app>
<note place="interlinear">b</note>
</app> Darauf wir ew erberkeit <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch aber
                            <expan>fleizziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wan uns kein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, <app>
<note place="interlinear">c</note>
</app> daz ir uns <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<app>
<note place="interlinear">d</note>
</app> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
                        pasche. </ab></div>
